{"type": "article", "id": 23191, "title": "如果在伦敦想吃火锅，可以试试这家“爽爽”", "description": "像日式回转寿司一样", "date": "2016-03-03T10:16:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 24312, "name": "回转寿司"}, {"id": 24313, "name": "回转火锅"}, {"id": 1788, "name": "食材"}, {"id": 2135, "name": "菜单"}, {"id": 2413, "name": "logo"}, {"id": 130, "name": "伦敦"}], "category": 17, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 486, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702141112KO7AiydoREPMG18W.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>对于国人来说，火锅到底有多重要？北京羊蝎子、四川与重庆的麻辣、潮汕牛肉……来自各地区的吃法闪耀着人民生活的智慧光芒。尤其是冷天时候，一群人哪怕约在家吃饭，都极有可能是煮煮火锅。<br></p>\n<p>前些日子，在伦敦的唐人街（Shaftesbury 大道上），开了一家<a href=\"http://www.shuangshuang.co.uk\">回转小火锅店“爽 Shuang Shuang 爽”</a>。思念这一口火锅味道的留学生可以去试试。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141103S3KzQ4hPODLUjYTn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">而所谓回转火锅，就是借鉴了日式回转寿司的设计，传送带上放好一碟碟的食材，每人面前一口小锅。不管是和朋友一起还是独自一人都很方便。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141104riNubYK0q2XVUcIm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141104PWVDfRjMyOLkc4sZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77659574\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141105MBYxsEHagIqbjFT1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77659574\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141105LQo1iRaPr346FV7v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77659574\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">在“爽爽”，传送带上有超过 50 种食材，和回转寿司类似，吃完后会根据不同颜色的碟子来收费。比如绿色的是 1.6 英镑、黄色的 2.3 英镑（目前有五种颜色）。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141106RTwWJ7P5f3hta8Hs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77659574\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">碟子上的透明的罩子保持菜品的新鲜，同时印有简化的 logo 显示所属的种类，还标注了要煮多长时间。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141106OoERAMwKr4vatSeC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23041475\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">整个店铺是由<a href=\"http://icodesign.com/work/shuangshuang\"> icodesign 公司设计的</a>， 保持了清爽感觉。并且找来了美国艺术家  Xochi Solis 来设计了专属的 logo、餐盘、菜单、字体等等。像店铺的 logo 就是以中文的“爽爽”两个字变形成火锅的模样。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141107DAhMnrcQS8GvXUkZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77659574\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141108RhK2vnOeLtGcXruq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77659574\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141108JZNHB1vVD6oFIiEO.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77659574\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">菜单设计也带点“中国风”：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141109J637pSYEDP92emCl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77659574\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141110Q0CeJLgA5IH4N6GK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77659574\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141111hCxets93uRydBw0M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77659574\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141111oGjZTiLRM0hfUNzX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77659574\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">但这家店的老板  Fah Sundravorakul 并不是中国人，来自泰国，这之前在香港开了三家餐厅。 他希望把中国最流行的火锅，用一种更现代的方式进驻伦敦，至少从店铺视觉效果看来还不错。</p>\n\n\n"}